text.tspan: Hack on the Hill (HOTH) is a 12-hour, beginner-friendly
hackathon designed to give beginners a glimpse into what
a real hackathon would be and feel like. During HOTH,
there will be workshops, mentors, and amazing prizes for
the best hacks. We will also be providing a selection of
hardware for hackers to check out and hack with. Learn
